description: Cali Love Food Truck is brought to you by acclaimed Chef Rudy Balch, who has taken his extensive fine dining experience to craft delicious New American cuisine, all made special for the foodies on the streets. His selection of sandwiches, sliders, and sides are made with fresh and local ingredients, slow-smoked meats, and copious quality. From the NorCal Reuben (with corned beef, spicy kimchi, swiss cheese, truck-made Russian dressing on grilled sourdough) to the Diner Burger (with perfectly seasoned Angus ground chuck, short rib, & brisket, topped with 18 month aged white cheddar, bacon, pickle, and Russian dressing) to black truffle-infused fries...when you try anything from this incredible truck, you’ll certainly be feeling the Cali Love.
name: Cali Love Food Truck
